{"tid":2420264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南非失業率達32.5% 為歷史新高","createTime":"2021-02-23T23:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T05:40:11.000Z","uid":30788,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"294ce8f209c04753f25315150a0928e5630660ff","tid":2420264,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:01:54.000Z","msg":"03:34 <br />\n據南非統計局當地時間2月23日公佈的數據，南非2020年第四季度的失業率達到歷史新高，官方失業率達32.5%。南非統計局2020年第四季度數據中，大量人口從原來的&ldquo;不從事經濟活動&rdquo;轉移為&ldquo;就業&rdquo;或&ldquo;失業&rdquo;。與此同時失業人口增加70.1萬人，達到720萬。與2019年同期相比，全國新增失業人口140萬人。出現這種現象的主要原因是受到疫情影響，很多已經退休的人員不得不重新開始工作贍養家庭，同時大量學生輟學，提早進入社會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c67c8998c669c083793f8a3f2e89e4f644820","tid":2420264,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />墮落之城"},{"pid":"d8178908bc31d17e76d7af0203c6583f652528be","tid":2420264,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"沽meli了"},{"pid":"2161827f5e247bfbba2b4f52cd37e6b778de7600","tid":2420264,"uid":105798,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"shithole country"},{"pid":"1f6b50cc3e58dc3d7ee2887f60bb31a624bc9004","tid":2420264,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:10:53.000Z","msg":"When there&rsquo;re black ppl there ate shit holes"},{"pid":"1aaf30665927855411175e65d75456dd74036d36","tid":2420264,"uid":64051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8178908bc31d17e76d7af0203c6583f652528be","tid":2420264,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"沽meli了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:11:01.000Z","msg":"MELI 定 JMIA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6096c9bcf9af170d170b006b193fe24a1bed0996